{"tid":1507961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外國讀書嘅巴打有野同你地講","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:09:26.000Z","uid":255628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"405eea541e5716771ade6ef402ee3d962fe96f81","tid":1507961,"uid":255628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"晨早訂左9月1機票翻加拿大多倫多讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講 作為一個土生土長嘅香港人<br />\n我真係無心情離開呢個屋企🇭🇰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱知道個日搞和你塞<br />\n慶幸個日我係朝早機 受嘅波及應該唔太大<br />\n<br />\n個日好多frd都翻去<br />\n但係佢地有啲唔好彩係晏晝機<br />\n有啲就開始抱怨 話點解要個日搞<br />\n之後我都嘗試安撫佢地叫佢地體諒下<br />\n我地作為香港人一定要為呢場運動著想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我想講<br />\n我並唔係反對咁多位搞集會<br />\n而係非常支持你地作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算我班機係晏晝 跟住飛唔到<br />\n我一樣唔會怪責咁多位 一齊和你塞埋又點話<br />\n為作呢場運動  再多嘅不合作運動都係必須<br />\n<br />\n我呢一走<br />\n就會走兩年<br />\n等我下次翻黎嘅時候<br />\n唔知香港仲會唔會係嗰個熟識嘅樣貌<br />\n如果可以嘅話<br />\n我會留守係呢個屋企 同你地繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"0903d667bacd7cdd7f421efe1731db6a03969473","tid":1507961,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=a8d424bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx